  "summaries": [
    {
      "id": 840801,
      "category": "team",
      "content": "An open redirect vulnerability was identified in Rocket.Chat. \nThe /_saml/sloRedirect/:provider endpoint includes the redirect query string value directly in the Location header for a 302 redirect without any server-side validation. Since this route is accessible without authentication, an attacker can leverage a legitimate Rocket.Chat domain to redirect users to an arbitrary external site.\nThis issue is fixed in v8.4.0. ",
